==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to chew''' ([[chews]], [[chewed]], [[chewing]])

#To [[crush]] with the [[tooth|teeth]] by repeated closing and opening of the [[jaw]]s; done to food to [[soften]] it and break it down by the action of [[saliva]] before it is [[swallow]]ed.
